name: Woman's path
description:
It's one of my subject to draw, paint, or woodcut works about my feeling as a woman. 

These are works that I need to continue moving forward and which are a bit like landmarks on my path as an artist and as a human being.

I don't think there is any added value to create as a woman, but the form of this expression can sometimes say something unique about our body and our relationship to the world. It is neither better nor worse, but it simply exists.
